content.rendered:
Directed by Binod Pradhan.

Written by Pooja Verma.

Cast Diganth(Aditya Sodhi). Anushka Ranjan(Anushka). Sonnalli Seygall(Rhea (as Sonalli Sehgal)). Karan Grover(Jay (as Karan V. Grover)). Rishi Kapoor(Luv Kapoor). Satish Kaushik(Ravinder Sodhi). Upasana Singh(Sweety Sodhi (as Upasna Singh)). Parmeet Sethi(Kumar). Kitu Gidwani(Amrita). Himani Shivpuri(Gulabo). Aru Krishansh Verma(Petha). Neha Tomar(Nikki). Ali Khan(Batli) . Dhritiman Chatterjee(Sid Kapoor). Tripta Lakhanpal(Biji)

Language Hindi.

Producers Anu Ranjan. Shashi Ranjan.

Production GR8 Entertainment.
